          "treatment": "Activate MTP. 1:1:1 ratio (PRBC:FFP:Platelets). TXA 1g IV. Limit crystalloid. Avoid hypothermia. Bedside calcium replacement (1-2g Ca gluconate per 4 units). Serial labs. Surgical/IR source control."
